.Dd $Mdocdate: August 14 2012 $
.Dt SILI 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sili
.Nd Silicon Image 3124/3132/3531 SATA controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "sili* at pci?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for SATA controllers using the Silicon Image
3124/3132/3531 SATALink chipsets.
.Pp
Although
.Nm
controllers are actual ATA controllers, the driver emulates SCSI via a
translation layer.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4 ,
.Xr scsi 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 4.2 .
.Sh AUTHORS
.An -nosplit
The
.Nm
driver was written by
.An David Gwynne Aq Mt dlg@@openbsd.org
and
.An Christopher Pascoe Aq Mt pascoe@@openbsd.org .
@


